      "content": "Please do not change your warfarin dosage without consulting your prescribing doctor first. Warfarin levels need careful monitoring because even small changes can affect your blood clotting time significantly. Your doctor will use lab tests to determine the exact dose required for your specific heart condition. It is best to discuss any concerns about dosage adjustments with your healthcare provider.",
